'''Mehdi Sadaghdar'''（{{Lang-fa|ﻣﻬﺪﻯ صَدَقدار}}，{{bd|1977年|1月13日||}}）[[youtube|youtube]]频道ElectroBOOM的所有者，是一名伊朗裔加拿大电气工程师<ref name="aksam">{{cite news|title=Göz göre göre çarpıldı!|url=http://www.aksam.com.tr/yasam/goz-gore-gore-carpildi/haber-241251|work={{tsl|en|Akşam||Akşam}}|date=2 September 2013|language=tr|quote=Kanada'da yaşayan İran asıllı bir mühendis Mehdi Sadaghdar....|accessdate=2020-07-27|archive-date=2020-02-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200222150930/http://www.aksam.com.tr/yasam/goz-gore-gore-carpildi/haber-241251|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last1=Dunn|first1=Michael|title=Engineer goes BOOM|url=http://www.edn.com/electronics-blogs/benchtalk/4433531/Engineer-goes-BOOM|work={{tsl|en|EDN (magazine)||EDN.com}}|date=18 August 2014|accessdate=2020-07-27|archive-date=2018-06-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180623033445/https://www.edn.com/electronics-blogs/benchtalk/4433531/Engineer-goes-BOOM|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last1=McNamara|first1=Paul|title=Video about ESD both shocking and funny|url=http://www.networkworld.com/article/2223771/data-center/video-about-esd-both-shocking-and-funny.html|agency=[[国际数据集团|国际数据集团]]|date=4 January 2013|accessdate=2020-07-27|archive-date=2016-04-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160408085512/http://www.networkworld.com/article/2223771/data-center/video-about-esd-both-shocking-and-funny.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
==生平==
Sadaghdar生于1977年，于伊朗出生，现居于[[加拿大|加拿大]][[温哥华|温哥华]]<ref name="facebook">{{Facebook post|ElectroBOOM|1582970691744067|I finally turned 40 (yes I'm old despite my...|Mehdi}}</ref><ref name="theprovince">{{cite news|url=https://theprovince.com/opinion/columnists/mehdi-sadaghdar-the-electrifying-birth-of-an-internet-celebrity|title=Mehdi Sadaghdar: The electrifying birth of an Internet celebrity|publisher=The Province|language=en|accessdate=2020-12-21|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108102307/http://theprovince.com/opinion/columnists/mehdi-sadaghdar-the-electrifying-birth-of-an-internet-celebrity|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他分别于1999年与2006年取得[[德黑兰大学|德黑兰大学]][[应用科学学士|应用科学学士]]学位与[[西门菲沙大学|西门菲沙大学]][[应用科学硕士|应用科学硕士]]学位。<ref>{{Cite thesis|degree=B.A.Sc|last1=Sadaghdar|first1=Mehdi|title=11-Bit Floating-point Pipelined Analog to Digital Converter in CMOS 1.8 μm Technology|url=http://summit.sfu.ca/system/files/iritems1/4362/etd1522.pdf|publisher=Simon Fraser University|date=2005|access-date=2020-12-21|archive-date=2017-08-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170816172209/http://summit.sfu.ca/system/files/iritems1/4362/etd1522.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Mehdi Sadaghdar M.A.Sc. Graduate 2000-2006|url=http://www2.ensc.sfu.ca/people/grad/msadaghd/|website=sfu.ca|publisher=Simon Fraser University|accessdate=2020-12-21|archive-date=2019-07-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190731115500/http://www2.ensc.sfu.ca/people/grad/msadaghd/|dead-url=no}}</ref>
===Youtube频道===
Sadaghdar自2012年开始经营ElectroBOOM频道，在该频道的视频中常常出现具有喜剧效果的[[电击|电击]]与[[火灾|走火]]事故，Sadaghdar有意的制造这些「事故」来展示不当操作的危险性<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.cbsnews.com/news/painful-lesson-on-the-difference-between-major-electrical-currents-ac-and-dc/|title=mPainful lesson on the difference between major electrical currents (AC and DC)|publisher=CBC News|language=en|accessdate=2020-12-21|archive-date=2019-07-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190703013419/https://www.cbsnews.com/news/painful-lesson-on-the-difference-between-major-electrical-currents-ac-and-dc/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="theprovince"></ref><ref>{{youtube|1-Smlsj76nU|Internet Fakery, The Bay Area Maker Faire and Presentation}}</ref>。截至2020年12月，ElectroBOOM有超过400万个订阅者，其中点击率最高的影片是「How NOT to make an electric guitar」<ref>{{youtube|TwIvUbOhcKE|How NOT to Make an Electric Guitar (The Hazards of Electricity)}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last1=Goodman|first1=William|title=How NOT To Make An Electric Guitar (VIDEO)|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2013/08/26/how-not-to-make-an-electric-guitar-_n_3818104.html|work=[[赫芬顿邮报|赫芬顿邮报]]|date=26 August 2013|accessdate=2020-07-27|archive-date=2016-09-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160927070653/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2013/08/26/how-not-to-make-an-electric-guitar-_n_3818104.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。Sadaghdar还会不时查看ElectroBoom Subreddit，回答粉丝提出的问题。此外，Sadaghdar偶尔会发布一些拆穿和批评[[偽科学|偽科学]]的视频<ref>{{youtube|Ok05GFoESGE|ORIGINAL CONCEPT: Reviewing Your Reddit Submissions}}</ref><ref>{{youtube|8uH74L6YtGU|Body Jump-Start and BioCharger RECTIFICATION}}</ref><ref>{{youtube|9gpjRy3uDUM|Is Space Travel Possible??}}</ref>

在Bilibili上，由FPS罗兹代理ElectroBOOM的中文翻译，在FPS罗兹的帐号发布<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.bilibili.com/read/cv750640|title=本人与ElectroBOOM频道的官方授权证明|website=Bilibili}}</ref>。
